-- Ally Chosen By Berkshire’s Forest River for RV Dealer Financing
-- B y   N o a h   B u h a y a r
-- 2012-05-22T14:07:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-22/ally-chosen-by-berkshire-s-forest-river-for-rv-dealer-financing.html
Ally Financial Inc., the bailed-out
auto lender, was selected by the Forest River unit at  Warren Buffett ’s  Berkshire Hathaway Inc. (BRK/A)  to provide inventory financing
for dealers of recreational vehicles.  Detroit-based Ally will participate in the interest
reimbursement program for dealers obtaining wholesale financing,
the companies said today in a statement distributed by Business
Wire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Noah Buhayar in New York at 
